Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.20,default,,0,0,0,,I can defeat that Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倒せる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの会長を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.77,default,,0,0,0,,I won't let go!\NOne more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:00.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,離さねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:01:00.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひと勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.55,default,,0,0,0,,The curtain rises on Kaiji's\Nassault on the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この黒幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長を討つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:09.02,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's final challenge begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の挑戦が始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.78,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:19.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうひと勝負だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.44,default,,0,0,0,,One more round, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:25.30,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きさま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長がお疲れだと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.05,0:01:28.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仰っているのが分からないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:28.74,default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you understand when the\NDirector said he was tired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:30.03,default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ったことか！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーむ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃がさねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーむ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.04,default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:44.27,default,,0,0,0,,Don't go too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:45.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,図に乗りおって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だあ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度勝負だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.28,default,,0,0,0,,One more round!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.62,default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きさま！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.70,default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずこの手を離してもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.56,default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, will you let go\Nof my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:06.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで食い下がられては
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.83,default,,0,0,0,,Since you refuse to back down,\NI have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方あるまい おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.30,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:13.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:13.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:10.91,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.82,default,,0,0,0,,- No! \N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつはもうこりごりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,断る！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.08,default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of that!\NI refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかそれでは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.91,default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NIn that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:24.00,default,,0,0,0,,- Bring the other...\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうそっちが用意するものは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:27.17,default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to accept anything\Nthat you've prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お断りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信用できねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.54,default,,0,0,0,,I can't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな仕掛けがしてあるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かったもんじゃないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:33.00,default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nsort of trap you've laid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:33.59,default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:37.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えがないとは言わせねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.60,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to spell it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.83,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:48.24,default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:50.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほどな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.62,default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.66,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji,\Nthat puts me in a fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしカイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:54.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは困ったのう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:58.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしろと言うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.82,default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly would you\Nlike me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:05.00,default,,0,0,0,,If E-Card is out and\Nso is everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカードも駄目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他に用意するものも駄目では
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負のしようがないではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.41,default,,0,0,0,,what will we gamble on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考える
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考える？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.83,default,,0,0,0,,Thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が何か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.98,default,,0,0,0,,I might have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:21.89,default,,0,0,0,,If he immediately proposed using\Nthe tissue box lottery gamble,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐにティッシュ箱を使った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを提案しては
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかにもこちらが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:22.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意していたようで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.31,default,,0,0,0,,the opponent would suspect\Na trap of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手に疑念を抱かせる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.29,default,,0,0,0,,The timing and context\Nof the suggestion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い出すタイミング
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間合い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.66,default,,0,0,0,,and also his expression\Nmust be as natural as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これらが自然に流れなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.40,default,,0,0,0,,Or he might blow this chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全て水泡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いわばこれもまたギャンブル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:35.34,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Nthis is a gamble in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:40.80,default,,0,0,0,,He has to take calculated steps\Nin drawing his opponent closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分と相手の間合い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呼吸をはかり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:42.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手を自分の思惑の中へ引き込む
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.29,default,,0,0,0,,...and finally, into his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:48.18,default,,0,0,0,,Paper towels...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:53.31,default,,0,0,0,,Just now, Tonegawa used those to\Nwipe the blood from the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき利根川がテーブルの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:52.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血を拭くのに使った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ペーパータオルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:59.31,default,,0,0,0,,That, and also... a ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:04:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:04:00.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,定規
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この２つを持ってきてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.86,default,,0,0,0,,Bring me these two items.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji gets to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.26,default,,0,0,0,,He starts making\Nthe lottery tickets,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.76,default,,0,0,0,,which are the basis for\Nthe victory he had planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てを支える土台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじ作りへ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:25.30,default,,0,0,0,,He was so nonchalent\Nabout it... How clever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さりげないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:29.21,default,,0,0,0,,Despite forcing the Director\Ninto a gamble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長に勝負を迫り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:29.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,承諾を取りながらも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.80,default,,0,0,0,,he still hasn't said a\Nword about the wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:32.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,掛け金については何も言わない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.61,default,,0,0,0,,This was just in case the\Nblack suits were to bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはこのあと黒服が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:38.34,default,,0,0,0,,...a tissue box without\Nthe fake winning lot inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじが仕掛けられていない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュ箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:43.81,default,,0,0,0,,Namely, one of the smaller\Nand more compact tissue boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧縮タイプの小さいサイズを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってきた場合に備えてのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:47.57,default,,0,0,0,,That would result in the gamble\Nbeing based purely on luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けのない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,運次第の勝負になった場合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.83,default,,0,0,0,,in which case Kaiji would\Nwager only a small amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,掛け金の額を低く設定する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.53,0:04:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやるかを宣言せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.89,default,,0,0,0,,Also, it was clever of him\Nto begin making the lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.66,default,,0,0,0,,...before declaring anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずくじ作りを始めたのもうまい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.84,default,,0,0,0,,If he were to propose a\Nlottery gamble right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし先に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじで勝負するって言ってたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.84,default,,0,0,0,,things might have been\Ncomplicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:04.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:04.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厄介なことになってた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例えば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじにする紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向こうが用意するとか言って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:08.61,default,,0,0,0,,For example, the opponent\Nmight bring out writing pads...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レポート用紙とかメモ用紙を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出してきたかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:13.04,default,,0,0,0,,...or note books\Nin order to prepare the lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.90,default,,0,0,0,,If so, the tissue box scheme\Nwould go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュ箱の仕掛けは無意味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.35,default,,0,0,0,,And that would be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万事休す
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.76,default,,0,0,0,,Even for the mark\Non the winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この当たりを示す丸の印だって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手に星だのバツにするだの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い出されたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.65,default,,0,0,0,,the opponent might request\Nto use a star or cross instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.37,default,,0,0,0,,That would spoil everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:37.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで全てが破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.18,default,,0,0,0,,That's why he must create\Nthe lots without a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も言わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:41.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじ作りなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.44,default,,0,0,0,,He's preparing the lots while\Nthe opponent is still unclear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:45.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手によく分からない状況での
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.78,default,,0,0,0,,...on what the gamble is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじ作り
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然そうしてるんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:49.10,default,,0,0,0,,All this isn't done randomly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てカイジさんの戦略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:52.44,default,,0,0,0,,Every detail is a part of\NKaiji's strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:59.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう戦いは始まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.69,default,,0,0,0,,The battle has already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:06.93,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.58,default,,0,0,0,,After drawing\Nthe fake winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕込んだ当たりくじを引いたあと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:17.94,default,,0,0,0,,how will I deceive them\Nout of finding the genuine one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱の中に残る本当の当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:18.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやってごまかすかだが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.15,default,,0,0,0,,After drawing the winning lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は当たりくじを引いたら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,派手に箱を掲げて振り回す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.99,default,,0,0,0,,I'll show off by hoisting it above\Nmy head and emptying its contents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじは部屋中に散乱する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.42,default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, the lots would\Nbe scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その散乱した中に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:32.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじがあるんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:31.77,default,,0,0,0,,But won't the real winning lot\Nbe among the scattered ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.55,default,,0,0,0,,That'd be as good as\Nletting them find it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じことじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前もって当たりくじを
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何枚か床にまいておくのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.92,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll leave\Nseveral other winning lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.83,default,,0,0,0,,...on the floor in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを作るとき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.66,default,,0,0,0,,While making the lots, I'll make\Na lot of "flawed" ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初の何枚かを書き損じて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:46.34,default,,0,0,0,,...and discard them\Nonto the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを床に投げ捨てる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるはずのない当たりくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つかっちゃまずいが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:50.54,default,,0,0,0,,If they find a winning lot that\Nshouldn't be there, it'd be doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何枚か印の付いたくじが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.35,default,,0,0,0,,But if they don't know how many\Nthere are on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:56.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,床に落ちてたとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:56.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかせる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.08,default,,0,0,0,,I'd be able to\Nbluff my way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが２枚だったか３枚だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんていうのは水掛け論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:07:00.59,default,,0,0,0,,So long as they don't know\Nthe exact number,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言い逃れる道はいくらでもあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.98,default,,0,0,0,,I can talk my way through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.59,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,懸命に積み上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.60,default,,0,0,0,,Now Kaiji is doing his best\Nto set up the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.36,default,,0,0,0,,In order to ensure his victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必勝のための仕組み
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鬼を殺す策略のかけらを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.60,default,,0,0,0,,he must piece together\Nthe plan to slay the devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔を伏しゆっくりと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:21.91,default,,0,0,0,,Pacing himself and ensuring that\Neverything is foolproof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確実に積み上げている
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.90,default,,0,0,0,,This victory can't be\Nbased on luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つことは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偶然じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:30.03,default,,0,0,0,,Winners don't win by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ者は勝つべくして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝っているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ力を気付かず戦えば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けて当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:34.78,default,,0,0,0,,Winners make preparations\Nto ensure their victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:39.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's not by coincidence but\Nrather, through concrete steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと具体的な行為の
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延長線にある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:41.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう意識を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'm nowhere near that level...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもっていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.20,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.36,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.53,default,,0,0,0,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでよし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ての通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.46,default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,\Nthere's one winning lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１枚当たりくじと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大量の外れくじ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:01.07,default,,0,0,0,,...amidst many blank ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:03.68,default,,0,0,0,,I'll mix this and\Nwe'll take turns drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを混ぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かわりばんこに引く
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に当たりを引いた方が勝ち
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.34,default,,0,0,0,,The first to draw\Nthe winning lot, wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シンプルだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:09.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.92,default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.03,default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is to find\Nsomething to put the lots in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何にこのくじを入れるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か袋か箱を用意してやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:15.42,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get him a bag or\Nbox of some sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.53,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.43,default,,0,0,0,,The trap is nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:25.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けは大詰め
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは中身が透ける
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:31.22,default,,0,0,0,,This won't do!\NYou can see through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.94,default,,0,0,0,,Also, this bag is your\Npersonal property.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このかばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともとそっちの持ち物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細工があるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きさまいい加減に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.88,default,,0,0,0,,You might have rigged it,\Nwho knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.84,default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとまっさらな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:41.72,default,,0,0,0,,It has to be something neutral!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:50.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:47.67,default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.80,default,,0,0,0,,We'll use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを使おう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.07,default,,0,0,0,,Not that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは駄目だ ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ開封されていない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.97,default,,0,0,0,,Get a new one that\Nhasn't been opened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新品がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.60,default,,0,0,0,,Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってきてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははあ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,Bring him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.15,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんの思惑通りいってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:14.71,default,,0,0,0,,Up till now, everything has\Ngone according to Kaiji's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題はあの黒服が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを仕込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:19.33,default,,0,0,0,,The issue is if he would bring\Nthe bigger tissue box variety...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:21.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大きい方のティッシュ箱を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:21.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持ってくるかどうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.75,default,,0,0,0,,...containing the fake lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.73,default,,0,0,0,,It was the only factor\Nleft to chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こればっかりは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人知の及ばない運の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.92,default,,0,0,0,,that he has no control over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし小さい方を持ってきたら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.48,default,,0,0,0,,What if he brings\Nthe smaller one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.68,default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでいいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.28,default,,0,0,0,,Will this do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.50,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:43.86,default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開ける前に見せてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.63,default,,0,0,0,,Show it to me\Nbefore opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさかとは思うが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,細工してる可能性だってある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:51.02,default,,0,0,0,,Although unlikely, it might\Nhave been tampered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいきさま
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きさまどこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見せてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:53.29,default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!\NThat's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.94,default,,0,0,0,,Let him see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりすぎたか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.53,default,,0,0,0,,Has he overreacted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かえって会長に疑われたかも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:09.33,default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Director\Nsuspects something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.27,default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちも確認してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.69,default,,0,0,0,,You should check it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:18.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてそんなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.01,default,,0,0,0,,Why did he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:21.59,default,,0,0,0,,What if he discovered\Nthe set-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことして
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕掛けを見破られたら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題なかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.59,default,,0,0,0,,There doesn't seem to\Nbe any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開封するぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,I'm opening it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.34,default,,0,0,0,,I see!\NCould this also be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさかこれも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.84,default,,0,0,0,,This too\Nwas part of Kaiji's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これもまたカイジの計算である
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.82,default,,0,0,0,,If Kaiji alone were to\Ninspect the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:47.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジだけが調べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:47.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不自然と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:47.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑惑を持たれる恐れもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.77,default,,0,0,0,,it would be unfair and\Nmight appear suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:52.58,default,,0,0,0,,Having one's opponent also\Nexamine the match conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手にも調べさせることによって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負前の双方の確認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.55,default,,0,0,0,,...is a necessary step.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必然の行為ととれる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:56.87,default,,0,0,0,,The main factor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして重要なのは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開封前に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手にチェックさせたこと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.81,default,,0,0,0,,...is for the opponent to check\Nthe box before it is opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:04.00,default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, if the box was inspected\Nafter it had been opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開封後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:02.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティッシュを抜いた後に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,箱をのぞかれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじの存在がばれてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.27,default,,0,0,0,,the fake lot\Nmight be discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:10.29,default,,0,0,0,,Both parties must check the box\Nbefore it is opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,双方がチェックするタイミングは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開封前しかない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジはまず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がチェックすることで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:15.92,default,,0,0,0,,By checking the box first,\NKaiji creates a natural flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自然な流れを作り
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手を巻き込み
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.53,default,,0,0,0,,This was to draw the\Nopponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ないという
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言葉まで引き出した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.30,default,,0,0,0,,...into agreeing that\Nthere were no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完璧だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:25.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごみさえ感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:24.31,default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect. I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ人間とは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ程までに用意周到に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:30.55,default,,0,0,0,,Are all winners so meticulous\Nin planning out every step?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考え尽くしてるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,置いてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,Put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意はできたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:43.70,default,,0,0,0,,Everything is prepared,\NMr Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.70,default,,0,0,0,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.58,default,,0,0,0,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:04.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駄目だなあこれは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:04.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.55,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白くない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.66,default,,0,0,0,,It's not interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手間取った割りに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりにも単純すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.87,default,,0,0,0,,This is too simple given\Nthe amount of effort you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大の大人が眠気を押して
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.01,default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough for two adult\Nmen trying not to fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明け方間近に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるほどのものではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.13,default,,0,0,0,,...in the wee hours\Nof the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:18.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.06,default,,0,0,0,,Then again, this was your\Npersonal request, Kaiji,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで私を楽しませてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たっての頼みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.60,default,,0,0,0,,and you gave me\Nso much entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やらぬとは言わぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.33,default,,0,0,0,,I won't refuse to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やるには条件が３つある
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:32.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,However, if I were to play,\Nthere would be three conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.09,default,,0,0,0,,Conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大したことではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.93,default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nit's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.17,default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you\Nhear what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞けば至極
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君なら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理解してくれることばかりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.58,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd find them\Nquite normal, Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ってみろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.27,default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,条件の１つ目は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:51.22,default,,0,0,0,,The first condition is related\Nto the rules of this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その当たりくじについての
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,取り決め
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかさま防止のためのな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.59,default,,0,0,0,,It's to prevent cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:55.38,default,,0,0,0,,To prevent cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:57.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかさま防止のため？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:57.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見てみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:57.10,default,,0,0,0,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この我々の運命を握る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじのかぼそさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.53,default,,0,0,0,,Our fates rest upon such a\Nfrail slip of paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさに吹けば飛ぶようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.78,default,,0,0,0,,which can be easily\Nblown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこちらでいろいろと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,保護せねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:07.51,default,,0,0,0,,That's why I must protect\Nmy own chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:12.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず第一に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:12.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,団子の禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.20,default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, it cannot be rolled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなものは丸めてしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指の間はもとより
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:16.14,default,,0,0,0,,Rolled up like this, it can be\Nhidden under your fingernails...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,爪の間にも隠せる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.48,default,,0,0,0,,...or anywhere in your palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな丸まった状態の
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:22.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:24.49,default,,0,0,0,,Hence, we'll not accept\Na lot that is crumpled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認めないことにしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを認めてしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いたふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.52,default,,0,0,0,,If this were allowed,\Nyou could produce a fake lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:33.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は髪の毛や耳の穴に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:33.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あらかじめ仕組んだものを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.80,default,,0,0,0,,...from your hair or\Nbehind your ear,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじと称して
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引いてくることもあり得る
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:37.56,default,,0,0,0,,while pretending to draw one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お分かりか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.37,default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほどな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,団子は禁止だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.12,default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:44.01,default,,0,0,0,,I accept that crumpled lots\Nwill not be allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ははは 付け加えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを引くときは当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:49.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕をまくり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:49.67,default,,0,0,0,,In addition, one's sleeves\Nmust be rolled up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに引く寸前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに指の股を開いて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.53,default,,0,0,0,,...when drawing from the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:55.40,default,,0,0,0,,and fingers spread for\Nthe other party to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手のひらのチェック
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文句あるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.15,default,,0,0,0,,No problem there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.16,default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では条件の２つ目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.86,default,,0,0,0,,As for the second condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは少々
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,虫のいい頼みなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:07.16,default,,0,0,0,,it may seem rather selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:10.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先行権をわしに譲ってもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:10.61,default,,0,0,0,,but I would like\Nthe right to draw first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何っ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.17,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょっぱなに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くじを引くのはわし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.91,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\NI'll be drawing the first lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ということにしてもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.17,default,,0,0,0,,I want you to grant\Nme this request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？馬鹿な！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうことは普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.91,default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:24.75,default,,0,0,0,,That's usually settled over\Na round of Rock Paper Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公平に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃんけんとかで決めるもんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっともだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが今回の場合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.91,default,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:32.75,default,,0,0,0,,But I've acceded to so many\Nof Kaiji's requests this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:33.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでわしはカイジ君の要望を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:33.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全面的に受け入れてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:36.37,default,,0,0,0,,Not only have I accepted\Nhis challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:37.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われるままに勝負を受け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:37.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらが用意したくじでの勝負も
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:39.10,default,,0,0,0,,I've also accepted the idea of\Na lottery gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:39.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け入れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我ながらあきれかえるほどの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:43.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お人よしぶりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.57,default,,0,0,0,,I've been kind-hearted so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなのに少ない確率とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.84,default,,0,0,0,,Even though the\Nchances are low,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:50.88,default,,0,0,0,,if Kaiji draws the winning lot\Non his first try,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょっぱなにカイジ君が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりくじを引きでもしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:57.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは一度もくじを引くことなく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:57.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負は終わってしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:57.17,default,,0,0,0,,the gamble would end without\Nme getting even a single try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりといえば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりの話ではないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.82,0:15:01.08,default,,0,0,0,,Well, that is something\Nthat's very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは避けたいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:05.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何としても
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.41,default,,0,0,0,,But it is what I wish\Nto avoid, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.83,0:15:08.17,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌なら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは降りるだけのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:13.09,default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it,\NI'll just refuse your gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:16.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:16.35,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:19.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足元を見やがって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.39,default,,0,0,0,,He's making use of the fact\Nthat I have no control over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっとも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちが先行と
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まってたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.60,default,,0,0,0,,In any case,\NI didn't plan to draw first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度くらいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.97,default,,0,0,0,,One draw should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.83,default,,0,0,0,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.00,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:33.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理解してもらえてありがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.93,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being\Nso understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて３つ目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の条件だが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:36.62,default,,0,0,0,,Now, the third and\Nfinal condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肝心な掛け金についてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.30,default,,0,0,0,,It's the crucial factor,\Nwhich is the wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君の持ち金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.48,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you have\N20 million in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつをそっくり賭ける
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.35,default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'll wager\Nthe whole amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足りんな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ？足りない？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:48.13,default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.43,default,,0,0,0,,Not enough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足りない分はわしの方で調整する
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:55.87,default,,0,0,0,,I'll make adjustments for\Nthe insufficient amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,調整？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.41,default,,0,0,0,,Adjustments?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:01.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずばり１億といかんか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.97,default,,0,0,0,,How about making it\N100 million instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.08,default,,0,0,0,,100 million...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:07.61,default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっそんな額
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:11.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むちゃくちゃだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.53,default,,0,0,0,,T-That's a ridiculous amount!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はした金では燃えん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.62,default,,0,0,0,,A meagre amount like that\Nis nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釣り合わぬ金額でわしにとっても
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.63,default,,0,0,0,,The amount is above\Nwhat you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間尺に合わんと分かっていながら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:19.62,default,,0,0,0,,...and might be a waste\Nof my time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:23.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,燃えぬギャンブルよりはマシ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:23.89,default,,0,0,0,,but it's better than a\Ngamble with no thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.04,default,,0,0,0,,- Bring that here. \N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっこいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:33.51,default,,0,0,0,,This man is up to no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自覚しておる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.15,default,,0,0,0,,I am well aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:39.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの脳は既に焼かれておる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:38.62,default,,0,0,0,,The fact that my brain\Nis messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:43.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常軌などというものは
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:43.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とうに失せておる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:42.64,default,,0,0,0,,I've gone off my rocker\Nsince a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通の凡庸な刺激では燃えん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:47.52,default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary stimulus\Nhas no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんの持ち金は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:51.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,2000万だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:51.24,default,,0,0,0,,B-But Kaiji\Nhas only 20 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.66,default,,0,0,0,,That's right,\Nhe doesn't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金はない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.28,0:16:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,差額8000万
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:56.75,default,,0,0,0,,I'll have Kaiji bet on\Nsomething else...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君には
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:59.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金以外を賭けてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:59.40,default,,0,0,0,,...to make up for the\Ndifference of 80 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金以外？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.50,default,,0,0,0,,Something else\Ninstead of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通１本につき
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど大きな値は付けんのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:07.40,default,,0,0,0,,Normally, I wouldn't attach such\Na great value to just one round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで勝ち残ってきた勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.72,0:17:11.43,default,,0,0,0,,But Kaiji is an exception\Nwho has won his way thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズとは格が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.01,default,,0,0,0,,He is of a different category\Nfrom those trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに敬意を表して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.40,default,,0,0,0,,And in order to show\Nmy respect for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.48,default,,0,0,0,,I've placed a ridiculously\Nhuge price on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:19.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,破格の値を付けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１本につき2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.24,default,,0,0,0,,Each one is worth 20 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:29.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし負ければ差額の8000万
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.10,default,,0,0,0,,And if he loses,\Nthe 80 million difference...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君がその指４本によって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:35.18,default,,0,0,0,,...will be repaid with\Nfour of Kaiji's fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,清算してもらおう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪くない話だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.77,default,,0,0,0,,Not a bad deal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.87,default,,0,0,0,,This time, if Kaiji wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:49.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回カイジ君が勝てば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:49.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき橋を渡ったときのように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.88,default,,0,0,0,,I won't do what I did during\Nthe bridge crossing earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:53.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チケットによる引き換えだ何だと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:53.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ケチなことは言わん
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.16,default,,0,0,0,,where a ticket was given\Nin exchange for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:57.69,default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay you\Nright away in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その場できっちり払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キャッシュでな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うはあ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余程の幸運か才能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:04.60,default,,0,0,0,,Very good luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは人生何十年もの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:09.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,月日を費やしての労働
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.06,default,,0,0,0,,exceptional talent\Nor decades of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この３つのいずれかを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そそぎ込まねば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.83,default,,0,0,0,,If you have\Nnone of the above,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:16.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して得ることのできぬ金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:16.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,億
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:15.82,default,,0,0,0,,a sum of 100 million\Ncan never be achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが一瞬で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君のものになる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:21.34,default,,0,0,0,,And this can be Kaiji's\Nin an instant, if he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:22.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てばな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねじ曲がる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねじ曲がる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.27,default,,0,0,0,,Distorting, distorting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界をねじ曲げるほどの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.36,default,,0,0,0,,A powerful magnetic field\Nthat distorts its surroundings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:39.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強力な磁場を放つ金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.76,default,,0,0,0,,...is released from that\Nhuge sum of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空間を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:41.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の心を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.60,default,,0,0,0,,A demon that distorts\Nand draws in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねじ曲げ吸い寄せる魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.36,default,,0,0,0,,...its surroundings\Nand human hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:49.37,default,,0,0,0,,Money, the most dangerous,\Nyet the sweetest evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:51.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も危険で
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:51.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最も甘美な魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的な金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:54.38,default,,0,0,0,,A staggering amount\Nof 100 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが目の前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つかめば届くところにある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.78,default,,0,0,0,,...is now before his eyes\Nand is within reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:17.90,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ければ持っていかれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:26.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:24.90,default,,0,0,0,,His fingers are at stake\Nif he loses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.21,default,,0,0,0,,They will be excised\Nat the root!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,根元から４本！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:33.62,default,,0,0,0,,So, what will it be, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:33.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあどうする？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指をなくす上に2000万も取られ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.45,default,,0,0,0,,Not only will I lose my fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.00,default,,0,0,0,,but I'll lose\Nthe 20 million too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るのは借金と痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.25,default,,0,0,0,,All that will remain are\Ndebts and pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊滅的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.89,default,,0,0,0,,A complete utter defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手持ちの2000万が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みすぼらしく見えちまう大金
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.53,default,,0,0,0,,That huge amount makes\Nmy 20 million look shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:53.91,default,,0,0,0,,With my hourly pay of 900 yen,\NI'll never attain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時給900円の俺が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:57.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:20:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:20:00.44,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I work,\Nno matter how hard I work...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,働いても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:05.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たどり着けない金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.11,default,,0,0,0,,I'll never achieve that amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.96,default,,0,0,0,,With this, I can start all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけあればやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.42,0:20:10.82,default,,0,0,0,,I can start over from\Nthe beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の願い通りの人生にやり直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.95,default,,0,0,0,,I can rebuild my life again\Njust the way I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いけ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怖いのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.48,default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.77,default,,0,0,0,,The only thing to fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつが一回目に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりを引いてしまうこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:22.52,default,,0,0,0,,...is if he draws the winning lot\Non the first try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:27.10,default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely impossible but\Nhe has almost no chance of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:27.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あり得ないことじゃないが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:27.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,限りなく０に近い確率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:30.75,default,,0,0,0,,As long as I don't get unlucky,\NI'm sure to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな不運さえなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.47,default,,0,0,0,,I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.35,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.90,default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.76,default,,0,0,0,,- B-But... \N- It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:40.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし負けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.48,default,,0,0,0,,If you lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:43.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ考えないわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.42,default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it's not\Nentirely impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ける不運を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで考えないわけじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.65,default,,0,0,0,,It's not entirely impossible\Nto suffer bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:47.48,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:48.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:52.67,default,,0,0,0,,I can repaint my life again\Nfrom scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺の人生を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:53.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全に塗り替えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:57.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけの金を目の前にして
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.99,default,,0,0,0,,The money to do so\Nis right before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,降りられるか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:58.46,default,,0,0,0,,Can I let it pass by?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:05.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＧＯだ！俺は指を掛ける！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:01.50,default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:05.00,default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet my fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:09.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐふーひひひひー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くるか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.10,default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:14.80,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji's night of insanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その最終局面が動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.41,default,,0,0,0,,He makes his move during\Nthis final scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒼白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:45.81,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Investment
